     H            Y.
     F** UEXR48   **************************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : SET EDIPP47 (EDI TABLE)                                  *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 2022.05.05                                               *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                                 *
      **************************************************************************
      *  CALLING SEQ.
      *                    CALL 'UEXR48 '
      *                    PARM           $PRTN  10
      *                    PARM           $NONY   4
      *                    PARM           $SIRE   6
      *   IN  $PRTN  10A  DELIVERY CODE
      *       $NONY   4A  SHIP DATE
      *       $SIRE   6A  USER PART
     F**************************************************************************
     FEDIPP47 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *************************************************************************
     C                     TIME           SDATE
      *
     C           SVRTNR    CHAINEDIPP47              99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CLEAREDIPP471
     C                     MOVELSVRTNR    E7PRTN
     C                     MOVEL@NONY     E7NONY
     C                     MOVEL@SIRE     E7SIRE
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     E7CRHZ
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       E7CRTM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     E7CRME
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      E7CRPG
     C                     WRITEEDIPP471
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELEPRTNR    SVRTNR
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @SIRE
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
